data.description: WOW! Do not miss the opportunity of getting this beautiful home! Let's make this Christmas the most wonderful one for you and your family ! This 3 bedrooms 2 baths home is waiting for you !.  Tax records don't show them. Make this your home with the final touches. Amazing lot,  Large level yard ( front and back). Plenty of parking space. Large storage/shop building in the back. Three bedrooms, two baths, with open kitchen view to family room. Separated living room, front porch, and back deck to enjoy a peaceful, relaxing time. Location says all! Close to Carrollton downtown, Restaurants, West Georgia University, and more. Call now for an appointment and schedule your private view. This home is occupied, so make sure to call for an appointment. You have to see this one. I would love to show it to you. Your agent would be protected!
